WEBVTT

00:13:29.529 --> 00:13:30.775
you get:

00:13:30.799 --> 00:13:32.911
"The maintenance of what is right."

00:13:33.794 --> 00:13:37.560
And I think there are few things
more "right" in this world

00:13:37.584 --> 00:13:39.320
than bringing people together,

00:13:39.344 --> 00:13:40.646
than unions.

00:13:41.395 --> 00:13:43.892
And if we allow social media
to deliver that,

00:13:43.916 --> 00:13:47.854
then it can deliver a very powerful
form of justice, indeed.

00:13:48.477 --> 00:13:49.706
Thank you very much.

00:13:49.730 --> 00:13:56.615
(Applause)